        Changelog
        =========
        
        1.0b3
        --------------------
        
        - Support script(Python)
        
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
          from ngi.notify.datadog.dd import metric_datadog
        
          metric_datadog('plone.login_failed', tags={'user': request.form.get('__ac_name', '')})
        
        
